(25, 'iPhone 11 Pro Max 256GB', 1460, 6, 1373, 68, 'iPhone 11 Pro Max is a product for those who are looking for perfection during the phone experience. With this iPhone, Apple has reached its peak by optimizing all internal factors such as performance, camera, battery and design in the best way.', 'iphone-11-pro-max-256gb.jpg', 1),
(26, 'iPhone 6s Plus 32GB', 344, 9, 313, 68, 'Apple iPhone 6s Plus is the largest screen iPhone, allowing users to do more things on a large space. In addition, new features such as iOS 10, 3D Touch, Live Photos or excellent 12MP camera will bring you the most satisfaction when using a really high-end smartphone.', 'iphone-6s-plus-32gb.jpg', 1),
(27, 'Xiaomi Redmi Note 9 4GB-128GB ', 215, 7, 200, 68, 'The Xiaomi Redmi Note 9 continues the success story of the Redmi series, Xiaomi s best-selling phone ever. With incredible power, outstanding battery life and 4 professional AI cameras, the Redmi Note 9 will bring unprecedented experience to budget smartphone users.', 'xiaomi-redmi-note-9.jpg', 1),
(28, 'Samsung Galaxy A31', 279, 10, 251, 68, 'Owning Samsung Galaxy A31, you get a visual experience not inferior to any high-end smartphone with a brilliant 6.4-inch widescreen. In addition, the ability to take professional photos thanks to the four-camera cluster on the back is also a plus point not to be missed when it comes to the Galaxy A31.', 'samsung-galaxy-a31.jpg', 1),
(29, 'Samsung Galaxy S20+', 945, 9, 860, 68, 'Samsung S20 + super product has appeared. Show off your true level with a premium design, beautiful big screen, 5 professional cameras, and incredible performance.', 'samsung-galaxy-s20-plus.jpg', 1),
(30, 'iPad 2019 10.2 Wi-Fi + 4G 32GB', 601, 7, 559, 68, 'iPad 2019 10.2 4G Wi-Fi 32GB is the optimal iPad version for most users, with a handy 4G connection, a large screen, compatible with Apple Pencil and Smart Keyboard accessories.', 'ipad-2019-102-wi-fi-4g-32gb.jpg', 1),
(31, 'Huawei MediaPad T5 10', 215, 5, 204, 68, 'Huawei MediaPad T5 10 is an affordable tablet with a modern and luxurious design. It also features a large, vibrant display and good performance.', 'huawei-mediapad-t5-10.jpg', 1),
(32, 'Masstel Tab 10 Plus', 99, 3, 96, 68, 'The price is very affordable for users, but Masstel Tab 10 Plus has a modern and luxurious design. Besides, it has a large screen and the configuration is quite good for your entertainment.', 'masstel-tab-10-plus.jpg', 1),
(33, 'Samsung Galaxy Tab A8 (2019)', 159, 9, 145, 68, 'The concept of a tablet phone first appeared with Samsung Galaxy Tab A 8.0 (2019). This is a tablet capable of making calls and using all day with a screen and a huge battery.', 'samsung-galaxy-tab-a8-2019.jpg', 1),
(34, 'iPad Pro 11 WI-FI 4G 64GB', 1117, 2, 1094, 68, '11-inch iPad Pro brings a perfect experience in a compact device. Full-screen design, incredible power, FaceID face recognition and the most advanced technology ever.', 'ipad-pro-11-wi-fi-4g-64gb.jpg', 1),
(35, 'Acer Nitro AN515-43-R84R/NH.Q5XSV.001', 773, 5, 734, 69, 'In the 2019 Nitro 5 series, the Acer Nitro AN515-43-R84R is a top-notch gaming laptop using AMD s configuration, with a distinctive thin bezel design and impressive surround sound.', 'acer-nitro-an515-43-r84r-nh-q5xsv-001.jpg', 1),
(36, 'Asus TUF FX505DY-AL133T R5 3550H/8GB/512G SSD/15.6 FHD/AMD RX560X-4GB/WIN10', 816, 3, 792, 69, 'Asus TUF FX505DY-AL133T is a cheap gaming laptop but still possesses remarkable power thanks to AMD hardware, giving great performance in an attractive price range.', 'asus-tuf-fx505dy-al133t-r5-3550h.jpg', 1),
(37, 'Masstel L133/Celeron N4000/4GB/128GB SSD/DOS', 258, 11, 229, 69, 'Believe it or not, the laptop with just over 5 million dong has a beautiful, sleek monolithic aluminum design, good configuration with an SSD, that s what Masstel L133 gives you.', 'masstel-l133-celeron-n4000-4gb-128gb-ssd-dos.jpg', 1),
(38, 'Asus Vivobook X509MA-BR062T N4000/4G/256GB SSD/Win 10', 301, 15, 256, 69, 'Asus Vivobook X509MA-BR062T is a cheap laptop but still has a stylish design, a thin bezel screen and ultrafast SSD hard drive, meeting the learning needs, suitable for students.', 'asus-vivobook-x509ma-br062t-n4000.jpg', 1),
(39, 'HP 15s-du0059TU Pentium N5000/4GB/1TB/WIN10', 344, 18, 282, 69, 'HP 15s-du0059TU is a cheap laptop option suitable for students, students and office workers. The highlight of this laptop is its beautiful design, big screen but still very compact.', 'hp-15s-du0059tu-pentium-n5000.jpg', 1),
(40, 'Lenovo Ideapad L340-15IRH i5 9300H/8GB/512GB SSD/3GB GTX1050/WIN10', 773, 15, 657, 69, 'Lenovo Ideapad L340-15IRH-81LK019KVN is a serious gaming laptop really for gamers with all the power and performance needed to play today s popular titles. A full size keyboard with backlight around. And a sleek, fashionable appearance following the current design language trend.', 'lenovo-ideapad-l340-15irh-i5-9300h.jpg', 1),
(41, '4D RUN 1.0 LTD SHOES ', 236, 0, 236, 73, '4D RUN 1.0 LTD SHOES LIMITED-EDITION RUNNING SHOE WITH INNOVATIVE CUSHIONING. Made to steal the headlines, powered by the future. The 4D Run 1.0. A limited-edition colourway influenced by the hues of Miami.  Combining innovation with data to enhance performance, the creation of the 3D-printed sole is based on 17 years of athlete insights. Each thread is individually constructed millimetre by millimetre using engineered mesh.  A Parley Ocean Plastic® textile upper provides support, breathability and flexibility – all without compromising on style.', '4D_Run_1.0_LTD_Shoes_White.jpg', 1),
(42, 'ADILETTE COMFORT SLIDES ', 34, 0, 34, 73, 'ADILETTE COMFORT SLIDES ULTRA-SOFT SLIDES MADE FOR ENERGY RETURN. Slip into pillowy-soft comfort with these men s slides. They re made with a cloudfoam plus footbed so your feet feel energised after your swim.', 'Adilette_Comfort_Slides_Black.jpg', 1),
(43, 'PRIMEBLUE ULTRABOOST 20 SHOES ', 215, 0, 215, 73, 'PRIMEBLUE ULTRABOOST 20 SHOES INNOVATIVE RUNNING SHOES WITH PRECISELY PLACED SUPPORT. Confidence doesn t just happen. It has to be built one run at a time. adidas Primeblue Ultraboost 20 Shoes are your go-to training partner for your best runs. The stretchy knit upper allows your foot to move naturally, while the flexible outsole keeps your transitions smooth. So your run feels effortless and build reserves of confidence you can take with you back to the rest of your life.  ', 'Primeblue_Ultraboost_20_Shoes_White.jpg', 1),
(44, 'ALPHAEDGE 4D SHOES ', 322, 0, 322, 73, 'ALPHAEDGE 4D SHOES CROSS-TRAINING SHOE WITH A HIGH PERFORMANCE MIDSOLE Add an edge to your game with the new AlphaEdge 4D. Designed for peak performance during your cross-training workouts, this model features a 3D-printed midsole. The lattice structure was developed using years of athlete data to deliver precisely-tuned support and cushioning right where you need it. The process is called digital light synthesis - light creates the shape of the sole, heat sets it. This model features iridescent panels inspired by the galaxy. Our formula for the future.', 'AlphaEDGE_4D_Shoes_Black.jpg', 1),
(45, 'CONTINENTAL 80 SHOES ', 107, 0, 107, 73, 'CONTINENTAL 80 SHOES SHOES THAT RULE THE HIGHEST COURT. Get served. These  80s-inspired adidas Continental Shoes ace all your fave looks. The classic white leather is clean and simple, a perfect pairing for weekend sweats and jeans. The webbing stripe and textile lining are just bonus points.', 'Continental_80_Shoes_White.jpg', 1),
(46, 'Video Camera Camcorder Digital YouTube Vlogging Camera Recorder kicteck Full HD 1080P 15FPS 24MP 3.0 Inch 270 Degree Rotation LCD 16X Digital Zoom Camcorder with 2 Batteries(604s)', 76, 0, 76, 70, '[Multifunctional Camcorder]: This video camera max supports 1080P(15FPS) AVI Video Resolution, 24M(6000x4500) JPEG Image Resolution. 3.0 inch LCD Screen and supports 270°rotation, 16X digital zoom, built-in fill light, Anti-shaking, Face Capture, Beauty Function, Self-timer, Webcam function, Pause function, USB 2.0, TV Output and so on. [Webcam Video Camera]: The digital camera has a Webcam function. When you want to video chat with your friends or family but without a cam on your computer, you may need this function. By connecting the computer with a USB cable, then choose the “PC CAM” mode as a webcam. Please download the software “AMCAP” before using the PC-CAM function, then enter the video interface, and then you can video chat with your friends. [Pause Function]: The camcorder supports the pause function, a good choice for YouTube and Vlogging. You can continue the recording in the same File without restarting a new one. And then you can download the video to your computer through a USB cable and then edit it before uploading to your social media. [Recording While Charging]: The digital camera comes with two 1500mAh 3.7V rechargeable batteries(Model: NP-FV5) One full-charged battery can be sustainably used for 60-90 minutes. Or you can record videos while charging, in this case, you can record long enough videos as you wish and no need to worry about battery drains. The digital camera supports SD card 4GB to 32GB(The SD card is not included in the package, and please format the SD card before using this camera). [Portable Camcorder]: The camcorder is small and lightweight, portable for you to carry around. The camcorder can support external LED light and standard tripod but not support external microphone(LED light and tripod are not included in the package). If you have any problems or concerns, please feel free to contact us. Our friendly customer service will do our best to solve your problem within 24 hours.', 'Camcorder-Vlogging-Recorder-kicteck-Batteries.jpg', 1),
(47, 'Video Camera Camcorder with Microphone, VideoSky FHD 1080P 30FPS 24MP Vlogging YouTube Cameras 16X Digital Zoom Camcorder Webcam Recorder with Remote Control, 3.0 Inch 270° Rotation Screen', 90, 0, 90, 70, '[HP1080P & 24MP & 30FPS CAMCORDER] The camcorder has HP1080P resolution and 24.0 mega pixels. Optical image dimming technology exceeds international standards. Supports taking high-quality photos or videos. In terms of image, color, and optical performance, it is superior to others. 30FPS allows you to get smoother videos. Capture the most exciting moments. The equipped remote control allows you to control camcorder from a distance of 7 meters.  🔥[WEBCAM & MULTIFUNCTION]-The video camera can be used as webcam. Open the Youtube, Facebook and Instagram pages to live streaming. You can also make video chat with friends or family. The Video camera for youtube vlogging has 3-inch & 270-degree rotating screen. It also has 16X digital zoom, anti-shake, facial detection, facial beauty, built-in fill light, pause and other functions. The pause function allows you to pause recording and resume playback without starting a new file. 🔥[With MICROPHONE & ANTI-SHAKE]-The camcorder for youtube use XY stereo pickup technology. Eliminating noise and NCR noise during recording. Suitable for conference recording, classroom teaching, news interviews, wedding shooting, outdoor travel, song and dance shooting. Camcorder with microphone adopts 6-axis enhanced level image stabilization, which the anti-shake effect is better. 🔥[HOT SHOE & LOONG TIME SHOOTING]-As an advantage of VIDEOSKY, the video camera camcorder with microphone has a built-in fill light to make photos and videos better. This digital camera has a hot shoe mount on the top for external microphones and external fill lights (not included). The standard screw holes on the bottom fit most tripods (not included with tripods). The video camera camcorder for youtube vlogging It support recording video while shooting, no need to worry about battery drain. 🔥[IDEL GIFT & AFTER-SALE SE', 'VideoSky-micrófono-Vlogging-Camcorder-Grabadora.jpg', 1),
(48, 'Camcorder Video Camera YEEHAO WiFi HD 1080P 24MP 16X Powerful Digital Zoom Camera with Microphone and Wide Angle Lens Remote Control Lens Hood Infrared Night Vision YouTube Vlogging Camera Recorder', 170, 0, 170, 70, 'Camcorder with External Microphone: External Microphone Adopts X-Y stereo pickup technology, clear and stable sound image localization.It “built-in a rechargeable battery”,the battery charging interface is Mini USB,use the usb cable to charge it.It also built-in “power output function” is equipped with a dedicated charging cable to “charge the camcorder”(push the switch to the top.)The external microphone has \"Hot Shoe\": It can be used to connect to other equipment,such as fill light. Camera with Wide Angle Lens＆Lens Hood: The camcorder comes with a professional 0.39X super 2-in-1 wide angle lens (with macro lens).The super wide angle lens can be widely used for big scenery, such as Buildings, Landscapes.The focal lens of the macro lens is only for close-up shooting of the micro object,such as flowers.The camcorder comes with a lens hood.It can block excess light and protect your camcorder lens from accidental damage.It improves the photos overall color and contrast. WiFi& IR Night Vision Camera Camcorder: By WiFi connection,the camera can connect to the the smartphone.The smartphone APP can be used to control the camera,including browsing photo albums and downloading the files from camera to the Mobile phone or Tablet for sharing,as well as a remote control by the APP control.(Read the user manual to download the APP).Under IR Night Vision,the camera can shoot high definition image videos,work perfectly in the darkness,also shoot great in low light. Camcorder with Remote Control: The camcorder come with an infrared remote control(Not included the 2xAAA batteries ).Through the remote control buttons,take photoes and videos by yourself, control TV playback or pause the camcorder videos from the remote place(Within 10 meters).The camcorder suppor