(49, 'Canon VIXIA HF R800 Camcorder (Black) + SanDisk 64GB Memory Card + Digital Camera/Video Case + Extra Battery BP-727 + Quality Tripod + Card Reader + Tabletop Tripod/Handgrip - Deluxe Accessory Bundle', 309, 0, 309, 70, 'This Photo4Less Top Value Camcorder With USA Warranty and manufacturer s supplied Accessories Kit includes: Canon VIXIA HF R800 Camcorder (Black) - Sandisk Ultra SDHC 64GB 80MB/S Class 10 Flash Memory Card - Photo Video Quality Tripod Digital Camera/Video Carrying Case - Extra Battery BP-727 for Canon Camcorder - Hi-Speed SD USB Card Reader - 5 Piece Cleaning Kit - Tri-fold Memory Card Wallet - Tabletop Tripod / Handgrip Record up to 1920 x 1080/60p Video - Canon 3.28MP Full HD CMOS Sensor - DIGIC DV 4 Image Processor - 57x Advanced Zoom & SuperRange O.I.S. Capacitive 3\" LCD Touch Panel Display - SD/SDHC/SDXC Memory Card Slot - Highlight Priority Mode - Fast & Slow Motion Recording', 'Camcorder-SanDisk-Digital-Tabletop-Handgrip.jpg', 1),
